Articles.Content:
Oh, I do have the KCT window in KSC (build list etc.). I thought there was supposed to be some other one. So I guess it's not a bug (though not very intuitive either). But the lack of the editor window is very bad because I can't even build anything, with the Launch button disabled.

I understand that the flickering (that makes stock toolbar buttons and many windows invisible) starts when you have too many items in the editor. However, I only have very few as I've just started a career game. 

Edited October 25, 2016 by garwel

That's why I thought pictures would help

Your lack of the window in the editor is a BIG problem, though not one I"m able to reproduce even using the Blizzy's Toolbar mod. I think one of the other mods may be a bad build or otherwise causing a conflict someplace. Finding conflicts is always the most fun part From being heavily modded it doesn't sound like it will be easy to narrow down without taking a lot of time. The modded testing install I'm using has:

Toolbar, AntennaSleep, Atmosphere Autopilot, Audio Muffler Redux, Simple Cargo (AxialAerospace), Radial Attachment Point (BZ-1), CactEye, CommunityCategoryKit, CommunityResoursePack, ContractConfigurator [known to have unrelated problems, testing newer versions as they come out], PontractPacks, CorrectCoL, CrewLight, CriticalTemperatureGauge, CryoTanks, DecayingRTGs, DeployableEngines, Action Groups Extended, RCSLandingAid, Vertical speed control (Diazo TWR1), DistantObject, DMagicOrbitalScience, DMagicUtilities, EasyVesselSwicher, EnvionmentalVisualEnhancements, EVAEnhancementsContinues, EVAFuel, Firespitter, FlexoDocking, HeatControl, HPTechTree, Indicator Lights, KAS, KerbalAtomics, KerbalEngineer, KerbnecController, Kerbal Science Exchange (KerboKatz SmallUnitlites), KIS, KrakenScience, KRASH, KRnD, MechJeb2 (exp. dev build), MissionControllerEC, NearFuture Contruction - Electrical - ElectricalNRSs - Propultion - Solar - and Spacecraft, Handrails, Final Frontier, S.A.V.E., ScienceStationVAB, PartTweaks, PlanetaryBaseInc, RadioFreeKerbin, RCSBuildingAid, RealChute, AmpYear, DeepFreeze, IONRCS, RoverScience, SCANsat, scatterer, SmartParts, Solaris Hypernautics, StageRecovery, StateFunding, StationScience, StockVisualEnhancements, SurfaceLights, TarsierSpaceTech, TigerTech, TRP-Hire, UmbraSpaceIndustries, Undockinator, VanguardAstrodynamics, VanguardTechnologyes, WaypointManager, Workshop, XenonHallThrusters, and XyphosAerospace.

When I do modded testing I go big But these are ones not causing a known conflict with what you're experiencing, so one you have that is not on the list, or not up to date, is likely causing the problem.

Of these, most don't do anything with the Editor, with the exception of EPL (which displays its window), PDPN, Janitor's Closet, and TweakScale. I'll try removing these and check again.
Great starting point. I'll start adding some tomorrow and see if I can reproduce the problem if you haven't discovered it beforehand. The problem will be found!
